\noindent
The slot filling ability of an LM, i.e. predicting ``Paris`` for a pair (France, hasCapital), is essential for KBC. This is done by querying an LM using cloze-style statements, a.k.a. prompts, like ``The capital of France is [MASK].''[petroni] . The LM's goal is to predict the token at the masked position, i.e. the object.